        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/sgv/fbh/6041287460.html"></div>
        </div>
<b>Tenju Tea House specializes in teas made fresh to order made with premium loose leaf tea and ingredients. We offer both tea on the go and prepackaged loose tea and tea accessories to our customers.<br>
We are hiring baristas with potential managerial position. Our team welcomes anyone who is passionate about tea and customer service to be a part of us! <br></b><br>
<br>
<b>If you see this listing it means we are still hiring!!!</b><br>
<b>If you see this listing it means we are still hiring!!!</b><br>
<br>
EXPERIENCE IS A PLUS BUT NOT NECESSARY. TRAINING WILL BE PROVIDED. WE NEED SOMEONE WITH A PASSION TO LEARN AND CONTRIBUTE TO THE COMPANY<br>
<br>
<b>TEA BARISTA JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:</b><br>
- Provide excellent customer service 
- Prepare and ensure quality of drinks and food.<br>
- Memorize product descriptions and be able to sell packaged products<br>
- Maintain cleanliness of working area<br>
- Cashier (greet customers with big smiles and take orders) <br>
- Able to work at least 15 hours a week <br>
- Full time position also available <br>
<br>
<br>
<b>THE IDEAL CANDIDATE WILL POSSESS VALUES THAT INCLUDE:</b><br>
- Be passionate, friendly, and cheerful (very important!)<br>
- Must love tea<br>
- Must work under pressure in a fast pace environment<br>
- Must have reliable transportation<br>
- Respond to customer complaints<br>
- Insist on providing great customer service and have the ability to build and grow customer relationships<br>
- Work well as part of a team<br>
- Basic conversational Mandarin Chinese would be a plus but not necessary
<br>
Working hours are flexible. <br>
<br>
<br>
Contact us for interview. We look forward to having you!<br>
<b>WHEN CONTACTING US, PLEASE INCLUDE:<br>
- YOUR FULL NAME<br>
- POSITION YOU ARE INTERESTED IN<br>
- TIME YOU ARE AVAILABLE TO WORK<br>
- LANGUAGES SPOKEN<br>
- ANY OTHER INFORMATION YOU DEEM RELEVANT</b><br>
<br>
<br>
<b>Email and/or text (626-788-1832) works better. (If you decide to text, please do it between 8AM-12Midnight) Due to the popularity of Craigslist, we will not be able to answer your calls. We will contact you once we get your information through email or text. Thank you!</b>    </section>

<ul class="notices">
            <li>Principals only. Recruiters, please don't contact this job poster.</li>
            <li>do NOT contact us with unsolicited services or offers</li>
</ul>

